name: paper cut style tiger year 2022
description:
This will be the Year of the Tiger, according to the Chinese zodiac, with the year lasting from 1 February 2022 until 21 January 2023.
People born in a year of the Tiger are predicted to be brave, competitive, unpredictable, confident and display great levels of willpower.
The tiger is known to be king of all beasts in China and comes third in the Chinese zodiac. Many Chinese children wear hats or shoes with a tiger image of for good luck. Now you can collect this item for your luck!
